<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/index/style_index_announce.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>


  <header class="nav">
    <div class="nav__inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav__logo">
        <svg class="nav__logo-icon" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
          <rect x="2" y="8" width="24" height="18" rx="3" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.15"/>
          <rect x="2" y="8" width="24" height="18" rx="3" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M10 8V6a4 4 0 018 0v2" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <path d="M14 14v4M12 16h4" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        복약안심서비스
      </a>

      <nav class="nav__links" aria-label="주요 메뉴">
        <a href="/index/index_about">서비스 소개</a>
        <a href="/index/index_HowToUse">이용 방법</a>
        <a href="/index/index_announce">공지사항</a>
      </nav>

      <a href="/login" class="btn btn--primary btn--sm">로그인</a>
    </div>
  </header>


<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">공지사항</div>
  <h1>새로운 소식을 전해드립니다</h1>
  <p>서비스 업데이트, 점검 안내, 이용 정책 변경 등 중요한 내용을 확인하세요.</p>
</div>

<main>
  <div class="notice-list">

    <% notices.forEach(function(notice) { %>
    <div class="notice-item">
      <span class="notice-badge <%= notice.isNew ? 'new' : '' %>"><%= notice.category %></span>
      <span class="notice-title"><%= notice.title %></span>
      <span class="notice-date"><%= notice.date %></span>
    </div>
    <% }); %>

  </div>
</main>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
  </div>

  <footer>
    © 2025 <span>복약안심서비스</span> | Team Jetson5 | 스마트 약상자 기반 복약 관리 플랫폼
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
